--? @shortdesc Orders an sgroup to attack the nearest squad in an sgroup. Each squad will individually attack the nearest 
--? target to themselves from targetSGroup. 
--? @extdesc targetSGroup - must be an sgroup with > 0 squads
--? queued (optional) - defaults to false. set to true if you want the command to be exectuted after other commands
--? @args SGroup sgroup, SGroup targetSGroup, Bool queued
function SGroup_AttackNearestSquadsInSGroup(sgroup, targetSGroup, queued)
